    "conteudo": "<!-- PBQE-C update 2025-12-04 -->\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"pt-BR\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <title>Central de Usuários • PBQE-C V2</title>\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\" />\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"usuarios.css\" />\n</head>\n<body class=\"page page-dashboard\">\n  <header class=\"topbar\">\n    <div class=\"topbar-left\">\n      <span class=\"topbar-logo\">PBQE-C V2</span>\n      <span class=\"topbar-module\">Módulo Usuários</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"topbar-right\">\n      <a href=\"login.html\" class=\"btn btn-ghost\">Sair</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main class=\"dashboard-main\">\n    <section class=\"panel-grid\">\n      <article class=\"panel-card\">\n        <h2>Cadastro de usuário</h2>\n        <p>Crie um novo usuário com e-mail e senha protegidos com Argon2.</p>\n        <a href=\"cadastro.html\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Ir para cadastro</a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"panel-card\">\n        <h2>Login</h2>\n        <p>Acesse o sistema usando suas credenciais já cadastradas.</p>\n        <a href=\"login.html\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Ir para login</a>\n      </article>\n\n      <article class=\"panel-card\">\n        <h2>Confirmação de e-mail</h2>\n        <p>Reenviar o código ou confirmar um e-mail pendente.</p>\n        <button id=\"btnAbrirConfirmacao\" class=\"btn btn-outline\">Confirmar e-mail</button>\n      </article>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"secConfirmacao\" class=\"panel-confirm\" hidden>\n      <div class=\"panel-card panel-wide\">\n        <h2>Confirmar e-mail</h2>\n        <p class=\"panel-text\">\n          Digite o e-mail utilizado no cadastro e o código recebido. Se precisar, peça o reenvio.\n        </p>\n\n        <form id=\"formConfirmarCodigo\" class=\"auth-form inline-grid\">\n          <div class=\"form-group\">\n            <label for=\"confEmail\">E-mail</label>\n            <input id=\"confEmail\" name=\"email\" type=\"email\" required />\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"form-group\">\n            <label for=\"confCodigo\">Código</label>\n            <input id=\"confCodigo\" name=\"codigo\" type=\"text\" maxlength=\"6\" required />\n          </div>\n\n          <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Confirmar código</button>\n        </form>\n\n        <button id=\"btnReenviar\" class=\"btn btn-text\">Reenviar código para este e-mail</button>\n\n        <div id=\"msgConfirmacao\" class=\"auth-message\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <script src=\"usuarios.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
  }
